\ \ \ \ $\ vi\ rules.conf
\ \ \ \ (review/modify\ the\ rule\ set)
\ \ \ \ $\ sudo\ install\ \-m\ 0600\ \-o\ root\ \-g\ root\ \\
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ rules.conf\ /etc/usbguard/rules.conf
